  "description": {
    "zh": "你看报纸了吗？最近，媒体一直在大肆宣扬蓝盔部队在塔科夫不作为，违反纪律规定之类的丑闻。\n混蛋！这些杂种记者。现在我们需要想个法子来摆脱资金断供的局面，这可不行啊朋友，这会对我们的利益造成损失。所以，我们需要另寻佳径来说服大众，蓝盔部队一直在践行自己的本分。你一定得去以UN主导的名义去镇压那些不法强盗犯罪集团的活动。我会提供给你一套必要的装备。但是如果你搞丢了，别贴着脸来找我再要一套。\n",
    "en": "Have you seen the news? Recently, media have been pushing the agenda that \"the Blue Helmets are not doing their job in Tarkov, do not follow the procedures\" and so forth... Those damn bastards, kurwa! I hate these journalist scumbags. We are one step away from losing financing, which, my friend, is the opposite of profitable for us. So, we need to convince the public that the helmets are actually doing what they promised to do. You must address the issue of eliminating the illegal bandit group activities but do so under the UN flag. I’ll give you the initial set of equipment you'll need, but if you lose it, don't come asking for more."
  },
